# Privacy Policy for GAssistant

GAssistant values your privacy.

This app may collect and process the following information solely for app functionality:

* Medication schedule data entered by the user
* OCR text extracted from prescription images
* Local notification settings
* Apple Health step count data (with user permission)

All personal data is stored securely on the device and/or secure cloud services used by the app.

We do not sell, rent, or share personal data with third parties.

HealthKit data is used only for displaying health-related information inside the app.

For support, please contact:
[support@gassistant.app](mailto:support@gassistant.app)
